      public SystemSettings(double holidaysIncrement, double childDiscount, double seniorCitizenDiscount, double premiumPrice, double standardPrice, double threeDIncrement, double blockBusterIncrement, double weekendIncrement)
      Constructor of a new SsytemSetting with the given input conditions from the user.
      Parameters:
      holidayIncrement - the increment if ShowSchedule falls on the holiday
      childDiscount - the decrement for children
      seniorCitizenDiscount - the decrement for senior citizen
      premiumPrice - the price for premium theatres
      threeDIncrement - the increment for 3D pricing
      blockBusterIncrement - the increment for blockBuster
      weekendIncrement - the increment for weekend
